---
import ZhLayout from '../../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="产品中心 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="史帝克全系列工业产品：静电消除系统、工业清洁机、精密CNC零件和自动化设备，适用于电子、SMT、光学薄膜及精密制造行业。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/products"
>
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/all-products/all-products.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;"
  >
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker">史帝克产品中心</span>
      <h1>工业自动化全系列产品</h1>
      <p>
        静电消除系统、工业清洁机、精密CNC零件和自动化设备，适用于电子、SMT、光学薄膜及精密制造行业。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="products-overview-section">
    <div class="container products-overview-layout">
      <aside class="products-sidebar">
        <div class="products-sidebar-box">
          <h3>产品分类</h3>
          <a href="/zh/products" class="active-category">所有产品</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator">静电消除系统</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine">工业清洁机</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts">精密加工零件</a>
          <a href="/zh/products/automation">自动化设备</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="products-main">
        <!-- 静电消除系统 -->
        <div class="products-category-block">
          <div class="products-category-header">
            <h2>静电消除系统</h2>
            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator" class="products-category-link">查看全部 →</a>
          </div>
          <section class="apple-product-section">
            <div class="apple-card-grid">
              <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-g-series" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-g.jpg" alt="ST-G 智能静电消除棒" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
                <h3>ST-G 智能静电消除棒</h3>
                <p>高性能离子棒，实现稳定高效的静电消除。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-e-series" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-e.jpg" alt="ST-E 智能离子棒" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
                <h3>ST-E 智能离子棒</h3>
                <p>适用于小型工业集成的可靠静电控制设备。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-f-series" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-f.jpg" alt="ST-F 智能离子棒" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
                <h3>ST-F 智能离子棒</h3>
                <p>适用于连续生产线的快速响应离子化解决方案。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator/st-s200" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/static-eliminator/st-s200.jpg" alt="ST-S200 迷你离子风机" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">静电消除</span>
                <h3>ST-S200 迷你离子风机</h3>
                <p>适用于工作台和敏感应用的紧凑型防静电风机。</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <!-- 工业清洁机 -->
        <div class="products-category-block">
          <div class="products-category-header">
            <h2>工业清洁机</h2>
            <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="products-category-link">查看全部 →</a>
          </div>
          <section class="apple-product-section">
            <div class="apple-card-grid">
              <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.jpg" alt="偏光片精密清洁机" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
                <h3>偏光片精密清洁机</h3>
                <p>专为敏感偏光片表面的清洁稳定处理而设计。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine/fpc-4-axis-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/fpc-4-axis-cleaner.jpg" alt="FPC四轴高精度清洁机" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
                <h3>FPC四轴高精度清洁机</h3>
                <p>适用于柔性印刷电路应用的高精度清洁系统。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine/smt-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/smt-cleaner.jpg" alt="SMT在线清洁机" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
                <h3>SMT在线清洁机</h3>
                <p>SMT工艺和精密装配线的在线清洁支持设备。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine/pcb-cleaner" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/pcb-cleaner.jpg" alt="PCB表面清洁机" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">清洁机</span>
                <h3>PCB表面清洁机</h3>
                <p>PCB制造和检验阶段的稳定表面清洁设备。</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <!-- 精密加工零件 -->
        <div class="products-category-block">
          <div class="products-category-header">
            <h2>精密加工零件</h2>
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts" class="products-category-link">查看全部 →</a>
          </div>
          <section class="apple-product-section">
            <div class="apple-card-grid">
              <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/custom-precision-machined-parts" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-machined-parts.jpg" alt="定制精密加工零件" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
                <h3>定制精密加工零件</h3>
                <p>根据客户图纸和规格定制的高精度CNC加工零件。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled.jpg" alt="精密轴承支架" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">精密零件</span>
                <h3>精密轴承支架（CNC铣削）</h3>
                <p>高精度CNC铣削轴承支架，公差稳定可靠。</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <!-- 自动化设备 -->
        <div class="products-category-block">
          <div class="products-category-header">
            <h2>自动化设备</h2>
            <a href="/zh/products/automation" class="products-category-link">查看全部 →</a>
          </div>
          <section class="apple-product-section">
            <div class="apple-card-grid">
              <a href="/zh/products/automation/product-a" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-a.jpg" alt="扩散板清洗检验生产线" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">自动化</span>
                <h3>扩散板清洗检验生产线</h3>
                <p>集清洗、检验和连续传送为一体的自动化生产线。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/automation/product-b" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-b.jpg" alt="机器人自动上下料清洗机" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">自动化</span>
                <h3>机器人自动上下料清洗机</h3>
                <p>机器人集成，自动上下料，清洗效率高。</p>
              </a>
              <a href="/zh/products/automation/product-c" class="apple-product-card">
                <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-c.jpg" alt="偏光片吸收轴角度测量系统" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="apple-card-tag">自动化</span>
                <h3>偏光片吸收轴角度测量系统</h3>
                <p>高精度偏光片吸收轴角度自动检测系统。</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .products-category-block {
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .products-category-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    .products-category-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #111;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .products-category-link {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0071e3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .products-category-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</ZhLayout>
